# =============================================================================
# GitHub API token - DEV-ONLY fallback. See docs/adr/0003-token-handling.md.
# =============================================================================
# Token resolution order at runtime (ADR-0003):
#   1. localStorage key `github-pat` - primary, set via the in-app UI
#      (per-browser, per-user). Arrives in milestone A.6.
#   2. VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN (below) - build-time fallback for LOCAL DEV only;
#      logged with a console.warn when used.
#   3. Anonymous - unauthenticated requests (~60 req/hr) if neither is set.
#
# WARNING: Vite inlines VITE_* vars into the bundle at build time. Builds
# intended for public deploy MUST omit VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN so the token is
# never shipped to the browser.
#
# Create a token at https://github.com/settings/tokens (public_repo scope is
# enough for public repos). Copy this file to `.env` and fill in:
VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN=
